{"type":"message","id":"b7b6cd8c","parentId":"930451ee","timestamp":"2026-03-19T03:50:46.374Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:bcd5d811-787e-4d9a-852c-8c4555613fc0 每日新闻推送 - 9:00 AM] 获取今日国际新闻摘要并推送给用户。使用 news-summary 技能从 BBC、Reuters 等 RSS 源获取最新新闻，生成简洁的中文摘要（5-8条重要新闻），按类别分组（国际、商业、科技等），然后直接推送给用户。格式：\n\n📰 今日新闻摘要 [日期]\n\n🌍 国际\n- [新闻1]\n- [新闻2]\n\n💼 商业\n- [新闻1]\n\n💻 科技\n- [新闻1]\n\n来源：BBC、Reuters 等\nCurrent time: Thursday, March 19th, 2026 — 11:50 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-19 03:50 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1773892246372}}
{"type":"message","id":"db1c4c34","parentId":"b7b6cd8c","timestamp":"2026-03-19T03:50:56.546Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户设置了一个每日新闻推送的定时任务（cron job），需要在每天9:00获取国际新闻摘要并推送给用户。当前时间是2026年3月19日，但实际执行时间是11:50（比设定的9:00晚了）。\n\n我需要：\n1. 使用 news-summary 技能获取今日国际新闻\n2. 生成简洁的中文摘要（5-8条重要新闻）\n3. 按类别分组（国际、商业、科技等）\n4. 推送给用户\n\n首先，我需要读取 news-summary 技能来了解如何获取新闻。","thinkingSignature":"9e727e44dc6b8c0a300b774b196fe89d3ee8dc62efff453d4daffea1ef1341f1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_oxjwtciezcoj_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/AppData/Roaming/npm/node_modules/openclaw/skills/news-summary/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":64,"output":156,"cacheRead":24316,"cacheWrite":12456,"totalTokens":36992,"cost":{"input":0.0000192,"output":0.0001872,"cacheRead":0.0007294799999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00149472,"total":0.0024305999999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773892246374}}
